\c 9
\s Ukugcina iphasika
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi enkangala yeSinayi, ngomnyaka wesibili emva kokuphuma kwabo elizweni leGibhithe ngenyanga yokuqala\x + 1.1.\x*, isithi:
\v 2 Futhi abantwana bakoIsrayeli kabagcine iphasika ngesikhathi salo esimisiweyo\x + Levi 23.5.\x*.
\v 3 Ngosuku lwetshumi lane lwenyanga le, kusihlwa, lizaligcina ngesikhathi salo esimisiweyo; ngokwezimiso zalo zonke langokwemithetho yalo yonke liligcine.
\v 4 Ngakho uMozisi wakhuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli, ukuthi bagcine iphasika.
\v 5 Basebegcina iphasika ngosuku lwetshumi lane lwenyanga yakuqala, kusihlwa, enkangala yeSinayi; njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamlaya ngakho uMozisi, benza njalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 6 Kwakukhona-ke amadoda ayengcolile ngenxa yesidumbu, ukuthi ayengelakugcina iphasika ngalolosuku\x + 5.2; 19.11,16. Joha. 18.28.\x*. Asondela phambi kukaMozisi laphambi kukaAroni ngalolosuku\x + Eks. 18.15,19,26; 27.2.\x*.
\v 7 Lalawomadoda asesithi kubo: Thina singcolile ngenxa yesidumbu; sivinjelelwani ukuze singanikeli umnikelo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesikhathi sawo esimisiweyo, phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli?
\v 8 UMozisi wasesithi kuwo: Manini, ukuze ngizwe ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izalilayani\x + 27.5.\x*.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 10 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi: Uba ngulowo lalowo phakathi kwenu loba owezizukulwana zenu ezangcola ngenxa yesidumbu, loba esekuhambeni khatshana, uzagcina iphasika eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 11 Ngenyanga yesibili, ngosuku lwetshumi lane, kusihlwa, bazaligcina\x + Eks. 12.6.\x*; bazalidla lesinkwa esingelamvubelo lemibhida ebabayo\x + Eks. 12.8.\x*.
\v 12 Kabayikutshiya lutho lwalo kuze kube sekuseni\x + Eks. 12.10.\x*, bangephuli thambo lalo\x + Eks. 12.46. Joha. 19.36.\x*; bazaligcina\x + Gen. 17.14. Eks. 12.15.\x* ngokwezimiso zonke zephasika\x + Eks. 12.43.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa umuntu ohlambulukileyo, ongekho ekuhambeni, oyekela ukugcina iphasika, lowomphefumulo uzaqunywa usuke ebantwini bawo, ngoba kanikelanga umnikelo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesikhathi sawo esimisiweyo\x + 9.7.\x*; lowomuntu uzathwala isono sakhe\x + 5.31.\x*.
\v 14 Uba-ke owemzini ehlala njengowezizwe kini agcine iphasika eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngokwesimiso sephasika langokomthetho walo, uzakwenza njalo. Kuzakuba lesimiso esisodwa kini lakowemzini lakowokuzalwa elizweni\x + Eks. 12.49.\x*.
\s Iyezi elaliphezu kwethabhanekele
\p
\v 15 Langosuku ithabhanekele elamiswa ngalo, iyezi lasibekela ithabhanekele, ithente lobufakazi\x + Eks. 40.17,34.\x*; lakusihlwa kwakukhona phezu kwethabhanekele njengokubonakala komlilo kwaze kwaba sekuseni\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*.
\v 16 Kwakunjalo isikhathi sonke: Iyezi lalisibekela, njalo kwaba lokubonakala komlilo ebusuku.
\v 17 Kwakusithi lapho iyezi liphakanyiswa lisuka phezu kwethente, langemva kwalokho abantwana bakoIsrayeli basuke; lendaweni lapho iyezi elima khona, abantwana bakoIsrayeli bamisa khona amathente abo\x + Eks. 40.36; Nani 10.11,33,34.\x*.
\v 18 Ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* abantwana bakoIsrayeli basuka, langokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* bamisa amathente abo: Bahlala enkambeni insuku zonke iyezi elalihlala ngazo phezu kwethabhanekele\x + 1 Kor. 10.1.\x*.
\v 19 Lalapho iyezi lihlala isikhathi eside phezu kwethabhanekele insuku ezinengi, abantwana bakoIsrayeli bagcina imfanelo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, kabasukanga\x + 1.53.\x*.
\v 20 Kwasekusithi lapho iyezi liphezu kwethabhanekele insuku ezinlutshwana; ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* bahlala enkambeni, futhi ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* basuka\x + Jobe 16.22; Gen. 34.30.\x*.
\v 21 Kwasekusithi lapho iyezi likhona kusukela kusihlwa kuze kube sekuseni, lapho iyezi liphakanyiswa ekuseni, basuka. Loba kusemini kumbe ebusuku, lapho iyezi liphakanyiswa basuka.
\v 22 Kumbe uba iyezi lalihlala isikhathi eside phezu kwethabhanekele okwensuku ezimbili, loba inyanga, loba umnyaka, lihlezi phezu kwalo\x + Gen. 24.55.\x*, abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahlala enkambeni, kabasukanga. Kodwa lapho liphakanyiswa, basuka\x + Eks. 40.36,37.\x*.
\v 23 Ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* bamisa inkamba, langokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* basuka. Bagcina imfanelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi\x + 9.19.\x*.
